NBA Decision Tree Model

# front-matter
rm(list = ls()) #clear the workspace

library(tidymodels)  # for the tune package, along with the rest of tidymodels

# Helper packages
library(rpart.plot)  # for visualizing a decision tree
library(vip)         # for variable importance plots
nba <- fread('/Users/malcolmzerbe/practice_r/nba/project/volume/data/interim/nba.csv')

nba <- as_tibble(nba)
class(nba)
[1] "tbl_df"     "tbl"        "data.frame"
nba <- nba %>%
  mutate(TARGET_5Yrs = as.factor(TARGET_5Yrs))

# Make Valid Column Names 
colnames(nba) <- make.names(colnames(nba))

nba
set.seed(123)
nba_split <- initial_split(nba, strata = TARGET_5Yrs)
nba_train <- training(nba_split)
nba_test <- testing(nba_split)
# training set proportions by response
nba_train %>% 
  count(TARGET_5Yrs) %>% 
  mutate(prop = n/sum(n))

# test set proportions by response
nba_test  %>% 
  count(TARGET_5Yrs) %>% 
  mutate(prop = n/sum(n))
tune_spec <- decision_tree(
                cost_complexity = tune(),
                tree_depth = tune(),
                min_n = tune()
              ) %>%
             set_engine("rpart") %>%
             set_mode("classification")

tune_spec
Decision Tree Model Specification (classification)

Main Arguments:
  cost_complexity = tune()
  tree_depth = tune()
  min_n = tune()

Computational engine: rpart 
tree_grid <- grid_regular(cost_complexity(),
                          tree_depth(),
                          min_n(),
                          levels = 5)

tree_grid
tree_grid %>%
  count(cost_complexity)

tree_grid %>%
  count(tree_depth)

tree_grid %>%
  count(min_n)
set.seed(234)
nba_folds <- vfold_cv(nba_train)
nba_folds
#  10-fold cross-validation 
set.seed(345)

tree_wf <- workflow() %>%
  add_model(tune_spec) %>%
  add_formula(TARGET_5Yrs ~ .)

tree_res <-
  tree_wf %>%
  tune_grid(
      resamples = nba_folds,
      grid = tree_grid,
      control = control_grid(save_pred = TRUE),
      metrics = metric_set(roc_auc)
      )

tree_res
# Tuning results
# 10-fold cross-validation 
tree_res %>%
  collect_metrics
#tree_res %>%
  #collect_metrics() %>%
  #mutate(tree_depth = factor(tree_depth)) %>%
  #ggplot(aes(cost_complexity, mean, color = tree_depth)) +
  #geom_line(size = 1.5, alpha = 0.6) +
  #geom_point(size = 2) +
  #facet_wrap(~ .metric, scales = "free", nrow = 2) +
  #scale_x_log10(labels = scales::label_number()) +
  #scale_color_viridis_d(option = "plasma", begin = .9, end = 0)
tree_res %>%
  show_best("roc_auc")
best_tree <- tree_res %>%
  select_best("roc_auc")

best_tree
dt_auc <-
  tree_res %>%
  collect_predictions(parameters = best_tree) %>%
  roc_curve(TARGET_5Yrs, .pred_0) %>%
  mutate(model = "Decision Tree")

autoplot(dt_auc)


library(data.table)
fwrite(dt_auc,'/Users/malcolmzerbe/practice_r/nba/project/volume/data/processed/dt_auc.csv')
dt_final_wf <-
  tree_wf %>%
  finalize_workflow(best_tree)

dt_final_wf
 Workflow 
Preprocessor: Formula
Model: decision_tree()

 Preprocessor 
TARGET_5Yrs ~ .

 Model 
Decision Tree Model Specification (classification)

Main Arguments:
  cost_complexity = 1e-10
  tree_depth = 15
  min_n = 40

Computational engine: rpart 
dt_final_fit <-
  dt_final_wf %>%
  last_fit(diabetes_split)

dt_final_fit %>%
  collect_metrics

dt_final_fit %>% collect_predictions()
dt_final_fit %>%
  collect_predictions() %>%
  roc_curve(diabetes, .pred_1) %>%
  autoplot()
final_tree <- extract_workflow(dt_final_fit)
final_tree
final_tree %>%
  extract_fit_engine() %>%
  rpart.plot(roundint = FALSE)
final_tree %>%
  extract_fit_parsnip() %>%
  vip()
